===Interjection===
'''coi!'''
# (''archaic'') Cry of a [[huntsman]] to send the dogs on chase. 

===Noun===
'''coi''' ''m'' '''cois''' ''pl''
# (''archaic'') [[quiet]]
#:''Le coi de la nuit''
#::''The quiet of the night''

